high_descs: Turn left and face the table in front of you.
Take the spoon from the table in front of you.
Turn right and face the sink in front of you.
Wash the spoon in the sink in front of you and take it out.
Turn right then open the drawer by the sink to your left.
Place the spoon in the drawer and close it.
anns.task_desc: Place a clean spoon in the drawer.

high_descs: Walk forwards and then turn left to reach the wooden table.
Pick up the spoon laying on the table.
Make a right to reach the kitchen sink.
Rinse the spoon in the sink and remove it again.
Move to face the drawers below and to the right of the sink.
Put the spoon into the bottom drawer to the right of the sink.
anns.task_desc: Rinse a spoon to put away in the bottom right-hand drawer next to the sink.

high_descs: walk forward, turn left, walk to table
pick up the large spoon that is on the table
turn right, walk forward to the sink
put the spoon in the sink, fill sink with water, remove spoon
turn right, walk forward a few steps, turn to face left
open bottom drawer to put spoon in
